LODGE AGA Experience Demo
-------------------------

This is the first demo I made. It draws some figures on your screen and
cycles the 128 used colors. Of course you need AGA graphics to run this demo.
This demo runs in full speed on an Amiga 1200 with 2 Mb of FAST-ram.

Press the left mouse button to exit the demo.

