V1.1 - What's new ?

- After receiving feedback trough e-mail (thank  ya all) I got right to work
  to present an improved version of the demo...
- Effect 5 (Pixel raster) has been improved. It does not destroy the
  background anymore and is much faster as before.
- I made the color cycle routine slightly faster.
- The edge line effect has been made faster.
- Improved the parallax effect. It does a realtime flip-Y and starts at
  the bottom or at the top of the screen.
- The selection of a new effect has been made slightly faster.
- Removed a test at the check left mouse button procedure.
- The color cycle routine starts now almost inmediately.
- A new effect has been added : The invertor. It places a raster over the
  screen which inverts the colors.
- The web-effect is now much faster.
- Precalculation of cosinus table at initialisation.
- Added the luxaflex effect as a variation of the pixelize effect.
- Lodge Logo effect has been added: Draws an inverted Lodge logo. To make
  the precalculation section more interesting.
- Several hotkeys have been added :

	F1  - Lores screen
	F2  - Hires screen
	F3  - SuperHires screen
	F4  - No interlace
	F5  - Interlace
	TAB - Change colors

- Watch out !!! To quit the demo you must now press the right mouse button !!
- The sliding screen at the start has been removed.
- Color cycling routine has slightly been improved, some precalculation has
  been used.
- Removed a small bug in the web effect. The first selected color was the
  last in the color range and not the first.
- The web effect can draw the color ranges in two directions.
- Several hotkeys have been added :

	F6  - Slow color cycling
	F7  - Average color cycling
	F8  - Normal color cycling
	F9  - Fast color cycling
	F10 - Incredible color cycling

- Removed the second screen at the intro. There is now a window at the end
  of the demo. Use the left mouse button or time out to leave this window.
- Removed color 0 from the cycle range.
- Added color 0 flash
- Removed some small bugs. Cubes, Circles and the paralax effect are being
  drawn on the whole screen.
- The original TBL (The Black Lodge) logo was replaced by the (temporary) 
  logo with the   new name of our group: Lodge. This was done because of 
  the fact that there already is a Swedish group called TBL (The Black Lotus) which 
  was established long before our group. They asked us if we would change the 
  abreviation. We're no name thiefs, so we changed the whole name.

The next version... Will be even better (we hope)...